flowchart TD
    Start([Start Loop]) --> CheckState{State File Exists?}

    CheckState -- No --> Init[Initialize Reviewer Agent]
    Init --> DeepReview[Perform Deep Review: <br/>Standards, Corner Cases, Tests]
    DeepReview --> UpdateState[Save Review to JSON]

    CheckState -- Yes --> ReadState[Read Previous Review]
    ReadState --> ReviewTheReview[Review the Review: <br/>Find False Positives & Omissions]

    ReviewTheReview --> Compare{Discrepancies Found?}

    Compare -- Yes --> UpdateState
    UpdateState --> Start

    Compare -- No (Consistent) --> Finalize[Generate Markdown Report]
    Finalize --> Exit([Exit Loop])
